name: Access Denied (V)
Lore: 'The doors on Cloud City use a special computer controlled locking system, making them difficult to bypass without altering the security codes.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. At Cloud City sites, Stunning Leader may not be played and your non-[Permanent Weapon] Rebels of ability > 3 are immune to attrition < 4. (Immune to Alter.)',
